entries.journal_entry_description: Captain Typho has some unclassified Marine missions that need to be completed.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Captain Typho needs someone to infiltrate the Mauler Stronghold and destroy their cache of weapons. Start by making your way to the stronghold.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Find the Mauler's Weapons caches. Your may have to fight your way to it through the stronghold.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Good Work. That should keep them busy for a while, trying to accumulate more weapons. It should give us an edge in apprehending most of them before they can prepare an assault against any of our military sites.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Make your way back to Typho to complete this mission.
